  "description": "It\u0026rsquo;s been a couple (or few) months since I\u0026rsquo;ve sent out any sort of update, so there\u0026rsquo;s a lot I want to share and I\u0026rsquo;ll probably forget a lot.\nI\u0026rsquo;ve set up a YouTube channel. I\u0026rsquo;ve already uploaded a few videos you can stream there, and plan on uploading more as I get more comfortable having a camera in my face.\nMe and my family have started stream restoration on a segment of Phahin Sinte Wakpala (Porcupine Tail Creek).\n",
